<h1>Privacy Policies</h1>
<h3>Welcome to Emirati Coffee LLC</h3>
<p><span>This Privacy Policy is meant to help you to understand how we use and protect the personal information you share with us, what data we collect, why we collect it, and what we do with it. We want you to know that protecting your personal information is important to us, and we respect your privacy.</span></p>
