<h4>Cookies</h4>
<h5><span>What is a cookie?</span></h5>
<p><span>A cookie is a small file that is placed and stored on your browser or device by a platform. Cookies allow a website owner to distinguish the activities carried out from your device from other users of that website.</span></p>
<h4>Cookies</h4>
<p><span>When you visit our Shop, various Cookies can be sent to your device. These are the very light text files, where data including login information are stored, sent to your computer by the websites you visit.</span></p>
